(8, 'Trend Micro Apex One', 'Admin', '2022-01-04', '<div class=\"entry-header\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 41px; text-align: center; color: #696969; font-family: CerebriSans; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<h1 class=\"entry-title\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 16px; font-size: 40px; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0em; line-height: 1.4; overflow-wrap: break-word;\">Trend Micro Apex One</h1>\r\n<div class=\"entry-post-meta\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 14px; margin: 0px -8px;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"entry-content\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 30px; color: #696969; font-family: CerebriSans; font-size: 15px;\">\r\n<div class=\"richText section\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">\r\n<h3 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin: 0px 0px 18px; clear: both; color: #333333; letter-spacing: 0em; line-height: 1.42; font-size: 36px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">Automated, insightful, all-in-one protection</span></h3>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-top: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"responsiveColumnControl section\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">\r\n<div id=\"responsive-column-d3148208-d0db-4f6c-940f-f1a079f8c0c5\" class=\"row\r\n\r\n			medium-spacing global-margin-top-none global-padding-top-none global-padding-bottom-none global-margin-bottom-large\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-left: -0.9375rem; margin-right: -0.9375rem;\">\r\n<div class=\"col-sm-4 col-xs-12 col-md-4 column\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0.9375rem; padding-right: 0.9375rem; width: 266.656px; -webkit-box-flex: 0; flex: 0 0 33.3333%; max-width: 33.3333%;\">\r\n<div class=\"productDescriptionContainer vitl section\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">\r\n<div id=\"product-description-container9f86a994-ffa5-4e15-b40e-3bea5906b774\" class=\"product-description-wrap bg-full bg-ful