(7, 6, 'Endpoint Security & Protection Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-shield\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'An Endpoint Protection Platform (EPP) is a solution deployed on endpoint devices to prevent file-based malware, to detect and block malicious activity from trusted', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">An Endpoint Protection Platform (EPP) is a solution deployed on endpoint devices to prevent file-based malware, to detect and block malicious activity from trusted and untrusted applications, and to provide the investigation and remediation capabilities needed to dynamically respond to security incidents and alerts. They differ from commercial anti-virus software as they allow admins to manage all devices and perform investigation and remediation against threats.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the endpoint security solution&nbsp;leaders like&nbsp;</span> <a href=\"https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/business/products/user-protection/sps/endpoint.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Helvetica\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; letter-spacing: .4pt;\">Trend Micro</span></a><u><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Helvetica\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #1a0dab; letter-spacing: .4pt;\">,&nbsp;</span></u><a href=\"https://docs.broadcom.com/doc/symantec-endpoint-security\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Helvetica\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; letter-spacing: .4pt;\">Broadcom Inc.</span></a><u><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size: 15.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Helvetica\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; color: #1a0dab; letter-spacing: .4pt;\">,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.eset.com/us/business-solutions/endpoint-security/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">ESET</a></span></u><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646139042-68621808.png', '0', 1, 1),
(8, 6, 'Server Security & Protection Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-user-secret\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Server security covers the processes and tools used to protect the valuable data and assets held on an organization\'s servers, as well as to protect the server\'s', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Server security&nbsp;covers the processes and tools used to protect the valuable data and assets held on an organization\'s servers, as well as to protect the server\'s resources. It comprises tools and techniques that help prevent intrusions, hacking, and other malicious actions. Server security measures vary and are typically implemented in layers.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Server Security &amp; Protection Solution leaders like&nbsp; <a name=\"_Hlk95922484\"></a><a href=\"https://docs.trendmicro.com/en-us/enterprise/deep-security.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Trend Micro</a> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646139438-19407961.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(9, 6, 'Endpoint Detection & Response (EDR) Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-get-pocket\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR), also referred to as endpoint detection and threat response (EDTR), is an endpoint security solution that continuously', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Endpoint Detection and Response (EDR), also referred to as endpoint detection and threat response (EDTR), is an endpoint security solution that continuously monitors end-user devices to detect and respond to cyber threats like ransomware and malware.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Coined by Gartner&rsquo;s Anton Chuvakin, EDR is defined as a solution that &ldquo;records and stores endpoint-system-level behaviors, uses various data analytics techniques to detect suspicious system behavior, provides contextual information, blocks malicious activity, and provides remediation suggestions to restore affected systems.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Endpoint Detection &amp; Response (EDR) Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.trendmicro.com/en_my/business/products/user-protection/sps/endpoint/detection-response.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Trend Micro</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646200674-55778669.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(10, 6, 'Extended Detection and Response (XDR) Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-lock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'XDR (extended detection and response) collects and automatically correlates data across multiple security layers  email, endpoint, server, cloud workload, and', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">XDR (extended detection and response) collects and automatically correlates data across multiple security layers &ndash; email, endpoint, server, cloud workload, and network. This allows for faster detection of threats and improved investigation and response times through security analysis.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">According to analyst firm Gartner, XDR is &ldquo;a SaaS-based, vendor-specific, security threat detection and incident response tool that natively integrates multiple security products into a cohesive security operations system.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with Extended Detection and Response (XDR) Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://docs.trendmicro.com/en-us/enterprise/trend-micro-xdr-online-help/xdr-part.aspx\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Trend Micro</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646200926-9861655.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(11, 6, 'Email Security Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-envelope\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Email security is a term for describing different procedures and techniques for protecting email accounts, content, and communication against unauthorized', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Email security is a term for describing different procedures and techniques for protecting email accounts, content, and communication against unauthorized access, loss, or compromise. Email is often used to spread malware, spam, and phishing attacks. This is usually done using deceptive messages to entice recipients to divulge sensitive information, open attachments, or click on hyperlinks that install malware on the victim&rsquo;s device.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Email Security Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.trendmicro.com/en_us/business/products/user-protection/sps/email-and-collaboration/email-security.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Trend Micro</span></strong></a></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">, </span><a href=\"https://www.barracuda.com/products/email_protection\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Barracuda Networks</span></strong></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to &nbsp;provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '1646201097-32094664.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(12, 6, 'Data Security and backup Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-database\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Data security is the practice of protecting digital information from unauthorized access, corruption, or theft throughout its entire lifecycle. Data backup is a practice', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Data security&nbsp;is the practice of protecting digital information from unauthorized access, corruption, or theft throughout its entire lifecycle.</span> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Data backup is a practice that combines techniques and solutions are typically designed to&nbsp;help your backup server data to&nbsp;another local server, a cloud server, or a hybrid system.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Data Security and backup Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.acronis.com/en-us/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Acronis</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients</span></p>', '1646201384-2429461.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(13, 6, 'SoC Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-soundcloud\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'A Security Operation Center (SOC) is a centralized function within an organization employing people, processes, and technology to continuously monitor and', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A Security Operation Center (SOC) is&nbsp;a centralized function within an organization employing people, processes, and technology&nbsp;to continuously monitor and improve an organization\'s security posture while preventing, detecting, analyzing, and responding to cybersecurity incidents.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Rather than being focused on developing security strategy, designing security architecture, or implementing protective measures, the SOC team is responsible for the ongoing, operational component of enterprise information security. Security operations center staff consists primarily of security analysts who work together to detect, analyze, respond to, report on, and prevent cybersecurity incidents. Additional capabilities of some SOCs can include advanced forensic analysis, cryptanalysis, and malware reverse engineering to analyze incidents.</span></p>', '1646201788-46785572.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(14, NULL, 'Network Security', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yes', 1, 0),
(15, 14, 'Web Application Firewall', '<i class=\"fa fa-arrows\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'A WAF protects your web apps by filtering, monitoring, and blocking any malicious HTTP/S traffic traveling to the web application, and prevents any unauthorized data', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A WAF protects your web apps by filtering, monitoring, and blocking any malicious HTTP/S traffic traveling to the web application, and prevents any unauthorized data from leaving the app. It does this by adhering to a set of policies that help determine what traffic is malicious and what traffic is safe.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A web application firewall (WAF) protects web applications from a variety of application layer attacks such as cross-site scripting (XSS), SQL injection, and cookie poisoning, among others. Attacks to apps are the leading cause of breaches&mdash;they are the gateway to your valuable data. With the right WAF in place, you can block the array of attacks that aim to exfiltrate that data by compromising your systems.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Web Application Firewall leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.f5.com/products/security/advanced-waf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">F5</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646202313-93338097.png', '0', 1, 1),
(16, 14, 'Next-Generation Firewall', '<i class=\"fa fa-gg\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'A next-generation firewall (NGFW) is, as Gartner defines it, a deep-packet inspection firewall that moves beyond port/protocol inspection and blocking to', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A next-generation firewall (NGFW) is, as Gartner defines it, a &ldquo;deep-packet inspection firewall that moves beyond port/protocol inspection and blocking to add application-level inspection, intrusion prevention, and bringing intelligence from outside the firewall.&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A next-generation firewall (NGFW) is&nbsp;a part of the third generation of firewall technology, combining a traditional firewall with other network device filtering functions, such as an application firewall using in-line deep packet inspection (DPI), an intrusion prevention system (IPS).</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Next-Generation Firewall leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.paloaltonetworks.com/network-security/next-generation-firewall\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Palo Alto Networks</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>', '1646202591-78378731.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(17, 14, 'Web Security Gateway', '<i class=\"fa fa-th-large\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'A secure web gateway is a cyberbarrier or checkpoint that keeps unauthorized traffic from entering an organization\'s network. The web gateway only allows users', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A secure web gateway is&nbsp;a cyberbarrier or checkpoint that keeps unauthorized traffic from entering an organization\'s network. The web gateway only allows users to access approved, secure websites&mdash;all others are blocked.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Next-Generation Firewall leaders like&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.acunetix.com/blog/web-security-zone/web-api-security/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Acunetix</a></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646202910-22692453.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(18, 14, 'Privileged Access Management (PAM) Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-window-restore\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Privileged access management (PAM) is the combination of tools and technology used to secure, control and monitor access to an organization\'s critical information', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Privileged access management (PAM) is the combination of tools and technology used to secure, control and monitor access to an organization\'s critical information and resources. Privileged access control provides security teams with fine-grained governance over sensitive systems and the ability to monitor how privileged company resources are being used. PAM establishes policies and practices to ensure the security of sensitive data and administrative accounts.</span> <span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">A privileged management system secures your network and enhances visibility while reducing operational complexity.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Privileged Access Management (PAM) Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://arconnet.com/products/privileged-access-management\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">ARCON&nbsp;</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">, </span><a href=\"https://fudosecurity.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Fudo Security</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646203183-59727757.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
