(20, 19, 'Penetration Testing Solution (PT)', '<i class=\"fa fa-align-center\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Penetration testing is also known as pen testing or ethical hacking. It describes the intentional launching of simulated cyberattacks that seek out exploitable', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Penetration testing is also known as pen testing or ethical hacking. It describes the intentional launching of simulated cyberattacks that seek out exploitable vulnerabilities in computer systems, networks, websites, and applications. It&rsquo;s a planned &ldquo;attack&rdquo; on a computer system designed to find exploitable weaknesses that could lead to security issues.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Penetration Testing Solution (PT) leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.rapid7.com/solutions/penetration-testing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Rapid7</span></a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646203717-112173.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(21, 19, 'File Integrity Monitoring (FIM) Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-file-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'File Integrity Monitoring (FIM) solution, as the name suggests, closely monitors sensitive files (configuration & content files) and triggers an alert whenever it', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">File Integrity Monitoring (FIM) solution, as the name suggests, closely monitors sensitive files (configuration &amp; content files) and triggers an alert whenever it comes across unauthorized accesses, copies, downloads, and modifications.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif; color: red;\">&nbsp;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Vulnerability Assessment &amp; Management Solution (VA or VM) leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://nederlands.tripwire.com/products/tripwire-file-integrity-manager#:~:text=Tripwire%20File%20Integrity%20Monitoring%20%28FIM%29%20has%20the%20unique%2C,part%20of%20assessing%2C%20prioritizing%20and%20reconciling%20detected%20change.\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Tripwire</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646204764-14094518.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(22, 19, 'Two Factor Authentication Solution (2FA)', '<i class=\"fa fa-binoculars\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Two-factor authentication (2FA) is a specific type of multi-factor authentication (MFA) that strengthens access security by requiring two methods (also referred to', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Two-factor authentication (2FA) is&nbsp;a specific type of multi-factor authentication (MFA)&nbsp;that strengthens access security by requiring two methods (also referred to as authentication factors) to verify your identity. With two-factor authentication, you\'ll need to both provide a password and prove your identity some other way to gain access.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Two Factor Authentication Solution (2FA) leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://www.fortinet.com/resources/cyberglossary/two-factor-authentication\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Fortinet</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646206009-94650229.png', '0', 1, 1),
(23, 19, 'Security Information & Event Management (SIEM) Solution', '<i class=\"fa fa-unlock\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) is a software solution that aggregates and analyzes activity from many different resources across your entire', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Security Information and Event Management (SIEM) is&nbsp;a software solution that aggregates and analyzes activity from many different resources across your entire IT infrastructure. SIEM collects security data from network devices, servers, domain controllers, and more.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraphCxSpLast\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">We have partnered with the Security Information &amp; Event Management (SIEM) Solution leaders like&nbsp;</span><a href=\"https://logrhythm.com/what-is-siem/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">LogRhythm</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">, </span><a href=\"https://cybersecurity.att.com/solutions/siem-platform-solutions\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">AT&amp;T Cybersecurity</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">, </span><a href=\"https://varularora.medium.com/wazuh-security-information-and-event-management-siem-for-small-and-medium-sized-enterprises-b2cf1cc7ce0c\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Wazuh</span></a><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\"> to provide the highest quality solution to our clients.</span></p>', '1646206867-68660192.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(24, NULL, 'Cloud Security', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Yes', 1, 0),
(25, 24, 'Cloud Security Posture Management', '<i class=\"fa fa-cloud\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Cloud Security Posture Management (CSPM) is a market segment for IT security tools that are designed to identify misconfiguration issues and compliance risks in', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Cloud Security Posture Management (CSPM) is a market segment for IT security tools that are&nbsp;designed to identify misconfiguration issues and compliance risks in the cloud. An important purpose of CSPM programming is to continuously monitor cloud infrastructure for gaps in security policy enforcement.</span></p>', '1646207088-21568895.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(26, 24, 'Cloud Workload Protection', '<i class=\"fa fa-folder-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Cloud workload protection is the process of keeping workloads that move across different cloud environments secure. To defend themselves against cyber-attacks,', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Cloud workload protection is&nbsp;the process of keeping workloads that move across different cloud environments secure. To defend themselves against cyber-attacks, businesses using private and public clouds need to focus on protecting themselves from harm at the workload level, not just at the endpoint.</span></p>', '1646208341-59643538.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(27, 24, 'Cloud Network Security', '<i class=\"fa fa-check-circle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Cloud network security is an area of cybersecurity-focused on minimizing the chances that malicious actors can access, change, or destroy information on a', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Cloud network security is an&nbsp;area of cybersecurity-focused&nbsp;on minimizing the chances that malicious actors can access, change, or destroy information on a public or private cloud network.</span></p>', '1646208756-93307766.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(28, 24, 'Cloud Identity Security', '<i class=\"fa fa-cubes\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Cloud Identity is an Identity as a Service (IDaaS) solution that centrally manages users and groups. When you adopt Cloud Identity, you can manage access and', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Cloud Identity is&nbsp;an Identity as a Service (IDaaS) solution that centrally manages users and groups. When you adopt Cloud Identity, you can manage access and compliance across all users in your domain. When you adopt Cloud Identity, you create a Cloud Identity account for each of your users and groups.</span></p>', '1646208940-46577373.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(29, 24, 'Secure Access Service Edge (SASE)', '<i class=\"fa fa-lightbulb-o\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'Secure Access Service Edge (SASE) is a security framework prescribing the conversions of security', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">Secure Access Service Edge&nbsp;(SASE) is a&nbsp;security framework&nbsp;prescribing the conversions of security and network connectivity technologies into a single cloud-delivered platform to enable secure and fast cloud transformation.</span></p>', '1646209127-42575617.jpg', '0', 1, 1),
(30, NULL, 'IoT Security', '<i class=\"fa fa-cogs\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></i>', 'IoT security is the practice that keeps your IoT systems safe. IoT security tools protect from threats and breaches, identify and monitor risks', '<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: \'Candara\',sans-serif;\">IoT security is the practice that&nbsp;keeps your IoT systems safe. IoT security tools protect from threats and breaches, identify and monitor risks and can help fix vulnerabilities. IoT security ensures the availability, integrity, and confidentiality of your IoT solution.</span></p>', '1646209339-77379840.jpg', 'Yes', 1, 0);
