(1, 'Respect for Honesty and Transparency', 'Creating content your audience loves takes time, but making it profitable shouldnt.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">In the course of representing a work seeker or client, <strong>TSL</strong> staff shall not knowingly make a false or inaccurate statement, fail to disclose a material fact, or make a representation as to future matters without having reasonable grounds for making it.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">TSL staff must adhere to principles of truth in advertising and will only advertise positions, through any medium, for which they have documented permission to recruit.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">All fees, charges and service provided must be explicitly and fully disclosed to clients prior to the acceptance of an assignment, or prior to any work being undertaken for a client.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">TSL staff should document all key stages of the recruitment process in line with relevant legislation and good practice guidance.</span></p>', '1636355147-90002049.jpg', 1);
