(4, 'Child Education', 'Bangladesh is over populated country where most of the people are depended on agricultural work in the rural area. They dont do any other sort of work or they dont have any other source of income.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Bangladesh is over populated country where most of the people are depended on agricultural work in the rural area. They dont do any other sort of work or they dont have any other source of income. However, they are large in numbers and have a big family to feed. The entire family is depended on only one earning figure, which is not enough for the entire family and then they choose the hardest path. They choose money over education. This is the common scenery of our country, mainly in the rural areas. Social voice foundation wants to give them monitory and all other facilities they need to develop their future.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1, '<i class=\"flaticon-gesture-1\"></i>'),
(5, 'Poor student', 'Child labor is very common in Bangladesh and the number of children is huge. Parents are not aware of the importance of their Childs education.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Child labor is very common in Bangladesh and the number of children is huge. Parents are not aware of the importance of their Childs education. They send them to work, so that they can earn money and contribute to the family. This practice is mostly common in rural and semi urban areas. However urban areas are also affected by the child labor problem. Children are working in dangerous conditions, living in the city, conquering appetite, neediness and brutality, adolescence for them has turned into an interminable battle to endure.</span><b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">There are huge number of people who are earning very low amount of money, do not earn or even unable to earn a single penny. &nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">This generation is the future of our country. If they cannot get the proper guidance and the monitory support our society cannot reach to its goal and our country will fall behind as well. We understand the need and importance of these needy people.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">We want to provide financial support to the poor for their medical expenses. We will collect volunteers from different region of the country, who will work for these people and have the same vision as us. Our volunteers will identify all the needy and poor people across the rural and semi urban area. They will provide all the necessary things they need. Also Doctors who could volunteer for the cause will be invited and notify time to time. Some of the main thing that social voice foundation will do for the poor students are:</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Donate supplies</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Donate clothes</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Give to local food support</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Student will get incentives (rice, wheat, pulse, vegetables) instead of education</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:36.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Donate technological device</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1, '<i class=\"flaticon-people-1\"></i>'),
(6, 'Orphan Children', 'We are blessed that we have parents in our life but there are many people who does not have this blessing. Parents are the first guidance of a child and they are the root of their bright future.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">We are blessed that we have parents in our life but there are many people who does not have this blessing. Parents are the first guidance of a child and they are the root of their bright future. However, people face different challenges in life and lost their parents, some may never see their parents or born as an orphan. These children are unaware of the true guidance they need for their future or even day to day life. Orphans do not only deprive from their parent guidance they also fell the gap of love in their life. Many children face early age mental health problem, physical issues or even teenage complexity but they dont know whom to tell or share their sorrows with. Social voice foundation wants to stand beside these orphan children.</span><b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp;</span></b><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">We want to know their need even more clear and better. In the core of each child there is a crave for home. Not only for basic needs and a place to rest, however for wellbeing and community. In particular: for adoration. Social voice foundation is committed to giving a caring home, profound consolation, and instructive open doors solely for young ladies deserted by their family. This empowers kids to rise above destitution and develop into minding and profitable individuals from their networks. We care for local children who would otherwise be left homeless for them we will manage vocational training facilities which aims to give the orphan children from the area the skills they need to find employment. It also operates a kindergarten pre-cadet school both for orphan boys and girls in the villages. Social voice foundation will assure quality education with morality to the children in a remote village and also in semi urban areas of Bangladesh.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>', 1, '<i class=\"flaticon-hand\"></i>'),
(7, 'Street Children', 'Among all the stages of education, primary education is undoubtedly the most important stage, because it is the initiation of process of making a person and a nation educated.', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\">Among all the stages of education, primary education is undoubtedly the most important stage, because it is the initiation of process of making a person and a nation educated. It creates the literacy base of a nation. Childhood education is the sound intellectual, psychological, emotional, social and physical foundation for children to become more productive citizens in adulthood. Therefore, in most developed countries primary education is considered to be more important than higher education. The Education program of social voice Foundation which is an NGO in Bangladesh that identifies such out-of-school children from remote villages, tribal areas and urban slums, and provides them quality education. In addition to this, it also looks after their health, nutrition, and holistic development through participation in co-curricular activities. Social voice foundation looks to change the lives of a large number of children in low-salary community by concentrating on proficiency and gender equality in education. Working in a joint effort with nearby networks, accomplice associations and governments, we create education abilities and a propensity for perusing among primary school children, and support girls to finish secondary school with the applicable fundamental abilities succeed in school and beyond. This educational program is a national level program of social voice foundation, which is focused on giving essential training and healthcare to unprivileged child. Social voice Foundation accepts that whether you are tending to healthcare services, neediness, populace control, joblessness or human rights, there\'s no better place to start than in the corridors of education.</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\">Make profile of street needy children</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\">Gather street educators</span><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:11.0000pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family: Wingdings; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-si