(8, 'Special Children', 'Education is both the methods just as the conclusion to a superior life; implies, on the grounds that it enables a person to acquire his/her occupation and the end since it expands one\'s mindfulness on a scope of issues ', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">Education is both the methods just as the conclusion to a superior life; implies, on the grounds that it enables a person to acquire his/her occupation and the end since it expands one\'s mindfulness on a scope of issues  from human services to proper social conduct to understanding one\'s privileges, and in the process advance as a superior resident. Yet, regardless of their conditions, they have not quit imagining. Their fantasies are as vivid as some other kid\'s and they have the same amount of potential to satisfy them. What they need is a reasonable possibility  a chance to go school, to sharpen their gifts, to try and have a glad and joyful youth that each kid merits. We wish for a world where all children can seek after quality instruction that empowers them to arrive at their maximum capacity and add to their networks and the world.</span><b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;\"><b><span style=\"font-family: Calibri; font-size: 12pt;\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></b></p><p class=\"16\" align=\"justify\" style=\"margin-left:72.0000pt;text-indent:-18.0000pt;text-align:justify;\r\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;mso-list:l0 level2 lfo1;\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:Calibri;mso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\r\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\">&nbsp;</span><!--[endif]--><span style=\"mso-spacerun:\'yes\';font-family