(2, 'ABOUT US', 'left', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">We do this every day. Listening to clients&rsquo; needs. Consulting with you and anticipating what it takes to make a truly successful hire. Tapping into a global network of relationships to find the best possible candidates.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">We&rsquo;ll take on your project as if we&rsquo;re on staff full time. Our team takes the time to get to know you so that the candidates we provide will fit the job description, the company culture, and the team you&rsquo;re creating.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">As a well-known integrated headhunting company in Bangladesh, Talent Sourcing Headhunting is specialized in providing excellent enterprises with high-end talent hunting, allocation and team building services. The Company is a famous human resource service provider and flagship in the domestic headhunting industry to provide one-stop total solution of high-end recruitment.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\">TSL has established the core advantageous industry including manufacturing, IT, communication, medicine, FMCG, real estate, energy and finance, etc.; and devote to providing 20 greatest enterprises in the Bangladesh market, we have recommended high-end posts like CEO, president, vice president/ deputy general manager, director, factory manager, senior manager, high-end professional and technical talents and other special talents.</span></p>', '1636874845-9887652.jpeg', 1, 'white', '1642245632-73571361.jpg', 1);
